<!--
  ╔════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════╗
  ║  SUGGESTED 6-BLOCK CASE STUDY STRUCTURE                            ║
  ║                                                                    ║
  ║  Used for cases 01–05 below. The Final Project (case 06) uses a    ║
  ║  longer V1 → V2 → V3 structure to show the iteration arc.          ║
